{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong><i>Crystal Conquest</i></strong> is a <strong>Free-To-Play</strong> VR game where you <strong>control the elements</strong> and battle for victory. Harness the power of fire, water, earth, and air in epic 3v3 MOBA-inspired combat or intense dueling modes! Team up with your friends against AI or choose to fight in PvP! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786380/extras/Crystal_Conquest_Gameplay_Jordan__3___3___1_.gif?t=1738130396\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Build your mage</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose the class that matches your playstyle and elements. Unlock class variants as you grow and customize your build.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786380/extras/Crystal_Conquest_Gameplay_Jordan__1___3___1_.gif?t=1738130396\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">H<strong>arness the elements</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Battle with elemental magic where each element has unique properties. Use earth, fire, water, and wind to block, dodge, and deflect your enemy's attacks. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786380/extras/Crystal_Conquest_Gameplay_Jordan__2___1___1_.gif?t=1738130396\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Grow in Power</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Level up and unlock even more epic spells that change how you control the elements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786380/extras/Crystal_Conquest_Gameplay_Jordan__1___1_.gif?t=1738130396\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Choose Your Battle Mode</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Battle in 3v3 matches to c